{"word":"Character","slug":"character","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Character</b> Of Saints:<br/> - Attentive to Christ's voice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=4'>Joh 10:4</a> <br/> - Blameless and harmless<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=2&verse=15'>Phi 2:15</a> <br/> - Bold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=28&verse=1'>Pro 28:1</a> <br/> - Contrite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=57&verse=15'>Isa 57:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=66&verse=2'>Isa 66:2</a> <br/> - Devout<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=2'>Act 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=12'>Act 22:12</a> <br/> - Faithful<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=17&verse=14'>Rev 17:14</a> <br/> - Fearing God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=3&verse=16'>Mal 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=2'>Act 10:2</a> <br/> - Following Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=4'>Joh 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=27'>Joh 10:27</a> <br/> - Godly<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=4&verse=3'>Psa 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=9'>2Pe 2:9</a> <br/> - Guileless<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=47'>Joh 1:47</a> <br/> - Holy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=7&verse=6'>Deu 7:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=14&verse=2'>Deu 14:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=12'>Col 3:12</a> <br/> - Humble<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=34&verse=2'>Psa 34:2</a